疫情下的深呼吸 | 希望能让孩子有个好一点的未来​。
Breathing deeply and suffering from the epidemic is hoping for a better future for its children.
协作者。
Collaborator.
协作者云社工                      。
Social worker Yun.
协作者云社工。
Social worker Yun.
协作者-云社工；功能介绍：志愿者信息管理、社会工作者信息管理、公益信息发布、社会工作专业交流。
Collaborator - Yun social worker; Function introduction: Volunteer information management, social worker information management, public service information release, social work professional exchange.
本文是协作者在“农民工抗疫救援行动”中，针对困境农民工家庭开展的个案访谈之一，旨在快速识别疫情中的脆弱人群及其需求，为疫情防控和救援工作提供参考，我们整理出来与你分享。
This article is one of the case interviews conducted by the co-authors in the "Anti-epidemic Rescue Operation for Migrant Workers," which aims to identify the vulnerable people and their needs in the epidemic quickly, and to provide reference for prevention, control and rescue work.
疫情下的深呼吸——困境农民工家庭个案实录（八）希望能让孩子有个好一点的未来口述者：郭玉（化名）山东籍打工所在地：青岛编者注：郭玉，44岁，山东籍在青务工人员，没有上过学，一家五口人。
(8) Hope that the children will have a better future dictator: Guo Yu (alias), the location of Shandong Province for a part-time job: Qingdao Editor's Note: Guo Yu, 44 years old, Shandong, a young worker, no schooling, five-member family.
郭玉在青岛生活了10年多，目前在青岛崂山区中韩附近居住，自己有头疼的毛病，厉害的时候每天都要吃止痛片，不敢去医院检查。
Guo, who has lived in Qingdao for more than 10 years, now lives near China and Korea in the Qingdao Laoshan area and suffers from headaches.
孩子爸爸打零工。
The father works part-time.
虽然不是很富裕，但郭玉认为，孩子们能在城市上学，接受好的教育就很知足。
Although not very rich, Guo believes that children can go to school in the city, receive a good education is satisfied.
希望孩子能够接受好的教育我是在大女儿出生以后，一家人一起来到青岛的，也有10多年了，期间二女儿、三女儿先后在青岛出生。
I came to Qingdao with my eldest daughter for more than 10 years, during which my second and third daughters were born in Qingdao.
大女儿已经上大学，正在商场实习，二女儿上小学五年级，三女儿上小学一年级。
The eldest daughter is already in college, working as an intern in the mall, her second daughter is in the fifth grade and her third daughter is in the first grade.
当初选择留在城市的原因是因为自己没有上过学，城市里的学校条件好，希望自己的孩子能够接受好的教育，有个好一点的未来。
The reason why they chose to stay in the city was that they had not attended school, that the schools in the city were good and that their children would receive a good education and a better future.
▲ 协作者社会工作者了解家里的生活状况（拍摄于2019年10月）孩子爸爸的身体还行，我自己有头疼的毛病，厉害了吃上药后就会好点。
The co-author's social worker understands the family life situation (filmed in October 2019) The child's father is in good health, I have a headache of my own and will feel better after taking the medicine.
自己因为害怕上医院检查出其他的毛病，所以头疼了就去药店拿止疼药，18元1盒的大约是20粒，头疼厉害的时候就吃上。
Afraid of going to the hospital to check out other problems, I went to the pharmacy to get pain medication, 18 yuan a box of about 20, eat when the headache is severe.
没有签合同也没有社会保险我因为没上过学，不认识字，换过的工作也挺多。
I didn't sign a contract and I didn't have social insurance because I didn't go to school, I didn't know how to read, and I had a lot of new jobs.
去年朋友给介绍的给婴幼儿洗澡的工作，每月工资大约是2800元，一直做到现在，但没有签合同也没有社会保险。
Last year my friend introduced me to bathing babies and toddlers, whose monthly salary was about 2800 yuan, and I still don't have a contract or social insurance.
孩子爸爸打零工，收入也不固定，好的时候一个月6000多元，也没有给自己投社会保险。
The child father works part-time, the income also is not fixed, good time a month more than 6000, also did not insure oneself social insurance.
我们夫妻只有在老家村里上的新农合，至于其他的商业保险，自己也了解了一点，但是没有能力去购买。
Our husband and wife only in the home village of the new farmers, as for other commercial insurance, I also know a little, but can not afford to buy.
包括孩子们，也只有学校的学平险以及老家的新农合，其他商业险也没有。
Including the children, only the school's level of insurance and the new home of the farmers, other commercial risks are not.
商场里人越来越少，才感觉到疫情的严重我家里有个旧面包车，一般过年都是正月初二开着车回去，因为疫情的原因，今年也没回家过年。
Shopping malls are less and less people, just feel the severity of the epidemic I have an old van, the New Year is generally driving back to the second day of the first month, because of the outbreak of the disease, this year did not go home.
我们大约是在1月20日知道这个疫情，不过当天感觉家长给孩子来洗澡还比较多，也没在意。
We knew about the outbreak on about January 20, but we didn't care that our parents would shower their children that day.
等到了1月21日，突然感觉商场人一下子少了，1月22日整个商场人更少，几乎没有人，才感觉到这个疫情的严重性。
By January 21, it suddenly felt like there were fewer people in the mall. On January 22, there were fewer people in the mall and almost no one felt the severity of the epidemic.
我在手机上关注了疫情的新闻，虽然不认字，但是感觉这个很重要，会经常性的看手机上疫情的进展情况。
I watched the news of the epidemic on my mobile phone and though I could not read it, I felt it was important to keep an eye on the progress of the epidemic.
只要能让孩子吃饱喝饱，心里就踏实现在我居住的村已经封村了，村里没有相关的疫情宣传，没有测量体温，也没有发口罩的，村里四周都是用铁皮围起来了，只让出不让进。
Now the village I live in has been sealed off. There is no publicity about the epidemic in the village. There is no fever and no mask in the village. It is surrounded by iron sheets and is only allowed to go in.
1月27日（正月初三）的时候还可以进出登记，现在是有身份证都不让进。
January 27 (the third day of the first month) can also enter and exit registration, is now not allowed to have identity cards.
我们现在只能在家不出门，少跟外面的人接触。
We can only stay at home and have less contact with the outside world.
让孩子们多吃饭、多喝水、勤洗手，出门一定要戴口罩。
Let children eat more, drink more water, wash their hands frequently, out of the door must wear masks.
▲ 郭玉家的出租屋（拍摄于2019年5月）我当年也经历过非典，那时已经在青岛了，目前的情况跟非典时差不多，也是有些紧张，但不是很厉害。
Guo Yu's Rental Housing (filmed in May 2019) I also experienced SARS at that time, already in Qingdao, the current situation is similar to SARS, but a little nervous, but not very severe.
唯一不同的是非典时只要有证件都可以正常出入居住的地方，现在这个疫情是不让出入，感觉是把人困在家里，有些不适应。
The only difference is that SARS can be normal access to the place of residence as long as there are documents, now the epidemic is not access, the feeling of people trapped at home, a bit out of place.
我自己感觉这个疫情怎么也要持续1-2个月，对生活影响感觉会很大，目前家里的米面剩余的不多，吃个三五天还没有问题。
I feel that this outbreak will also continue for 1-2 months, the impact of life will feel very large, the current home rice noodles are not much, eating for three or five days is no problem.
村里的市场也是关门，不敢出去，村里只让出不让进，担心出去以后进不来怎么办。
The village market is also closed, afraid to go out, the village only let out not to enter, worried about what to do after going out.
往年正常情况下，外地人都走了，村里的市场购买生活用品也是个难题。
Normally, outsiders have gone, and the village market has been a problem in buying supplies.
过去十几天，现在终于好一点了，村里有一个可以买菜的地方。
The past ten days, now finally better, there is a place to buy vegetables in the village.
家里的温饱基本能解决，但是最担心的还是经济来源，目前没有任何的收入，就靠着过年没回家的钱过日子，实在不行就需要跟自己的姐姐借一点，大人还好说不能让孩子跟着遭罪。
At home, food and clothing can be basically solved, but the main concern is the financial resources, there is no income, on the New Year did not live on the money, really can not do with their sister to borrow a little, adults are OK not to let their children suffer.
希望疫情赶紧过去，自己也好去上班挣钱。
Hope the epidemic quickly over, their own good to work to earn money.
假如这个疫情持续3个月或是6个月，我希望在生活上得到支持和帮助，只要能让孩子吃饱喝饱，心里就踏实，就不那么紧张了。
If the epidemic continues for 3 months or 6 months, I hope to receive support and help in life, as long as the children can feed and drink, the heart will be reassured, less nervous.
社会工作者手记不识字的郭玉，在外务工的时间里，经历过非典，现在再次经历新冠肺炎疫情，所以，在今天的通话中，感觉她对疫情没有太多恐惧，更加关心对生活的影响，尤其孩子的生活。
Social worker Guo Yu, who is illiterate by hand, experienced SARS during her time as a migrant worker and is now experiencing a new outbreak of pneumonia, so in today's conversation she feels less afraid of the epidemic and more concerned about the impact on life, especially that of her children.
百姓的安稳来自于衣食住行的顺畅，面对严厉的疫情防控，郭玉还是心怀希望，虽然自己一天学没有上过，但她知道教育的重要性，所以，就算生活再艰难，她还是希望孩子可以无恙！服务建议当下：1.普及新型冠状病毒防疫知识；2.提供基本救援物资，口罩以及消毒用品；3.了跟进村里封村的情况，必要时协助购买生活物品。
Despite the fact that she had not attended school in one day, she knew the importance of education, so she hoped that her children would be safe, even if life were as difficult as possible!
长远：1.普及社会保障和劳动合同法相关知识；2.提供就业辅导，拓展就业选择空间；3..继续提供助学救助。
In the long run: (1) popularize knowledge of social security and labour contract law; (2) provide employment guidance and expand employment options; (3) continue to provide educational assistance.
